      <title>美国对胡塞武装石油运输实施新制裁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/us-imposes-fresh-sanctions-targeting-houthi-oil-shipments</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国宣布对 10 名个人、船只和公司实施制裁，旨在切断也门胡塞叛军的商品收入，胡塞叛军多次袭击商业航运商，扰乱了红海的贸易流通。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/us-imposes-fresh-sanctions-targeting-houthi-oil-shipments</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 16:36:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>根据众议院计划，美国和以色列将进行年度隧道演习</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/us-israel-would-conduct-annual-tunnel-exercises-under-house-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国众议院军事委员会最新的8950亿美元国防开支法案草案将要求美国与以色列举行联合演习，旨在提高两国打击地下隧道武装分子和走私者的能力，这是对抗哈马斯和其他组织的关键优势的举措之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/us-israel-would-conduct-annual-tunnel-exercises-under-house-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 16:16:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>捷克人指责俄罗斯支持布拉格未遂纵火袭击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/czechs-blame-russia-for-backing-failed-arson-attack-in-prague</link>
      <description><![CDATA[捷克共和国指责俄罗斯组织并资助上周一名外国人在布拉格试图纵火焚烧公共汽车但未遂的纵火事件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/czechs-blame-russia-for-backing-failed-arson-attack-in-prague</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 16:07:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
