    <item>
      <title>勒庞 28 岁的政治继承人面临生死攸关的时刻</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/le-pen-s-28-year-old-political-heir-faces-a-make-or-break-moment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙决定提前举行大选，让法国陷入了不确定性 - 但这可能成就乔丹·巴德拉，玛丽娜·勒庞 28 岁、热爱自拍的政治继承人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/le-pen-s-28-year-old-political-heir-faces-a-make-or-break-moment</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 15:50:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苏纳克因英国减税和移民政策面临保守党的强烈反对</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/sunak-faces-last-ditch-tory-revolt-over-uk-election-manifesto</link>
      <description><![CDATA[保守党宣言的早期草案引发了外界不安，人们担心该宣言缺乏可能避免保守党在英国大选中惨败的重大承诺。内阁大臣们在最后一刻呼吁里希·苏纳克 (Rishi Sunak) 在宣言中添加新的减税措施和更严格的移民政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/sunak-faces-last-ditch-tory-revolt-over-uk-election-manifesto</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 15:49:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亨特·拜登的辩护因枪支案而中断，无需证词</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/hunter-biden-defense-rests-in-gun-case-without-his-testimony</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亨特·拜登的辩护团队周一在没有听取他的证词的情况下结束了他们的辩护，只留下了结案陈词，然后陪审团将被指示审议他是否违反了联邦枪支法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/hunter-biden-defense-rests-in-gun-case-without-his-testimony</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 15:08:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非议会准备本周选举总统</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/south-africa-s-new-parliament-to-hold-first-sitting-on-friday</link>
      <description><![CDATA[首席大法官宣布，南非议会将于周五复会选举总统，各政党将继续就组建新政府进行谈判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/south-africa-s-new-parliament-to-hold-first-sitting-on-friday</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 13:24:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟选举加剧政治风险 新兴货币下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/emerging-currencies-drop-as-eu-elections-add-to-political-risks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一，大多数新兴市场货币兑美元走弱，波动性指标跳升，因欧洲大选中极右翼势力崛起导致政治风险成为焦点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/emerging-currencies-drop-as-eu-elections-add-to-political-risks</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 10:51:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>舒尔茨在德国东部选举中再次遭遇惨败</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/scholz-heading-for-another-election-debacle-in-eastern-germany</link>
      <description><![CDATA[9 月份，德国总理奥拉夫·朔尔茨领导的执政联盟似乎将再次遭遇惨败。届时，德国东部三个地区将举行选举，而极右翼德国选择党是这三个地区最强大的政党。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/scholz-heading-for-another-election-debacle-in-eastern-germany</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 08:50:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
